================================================================================
Third-Party Components
================================================================================

Container Images
----------------
We rebuild and publish CloudNativePG operator images from upstream source
without modification.

CloudNativePG Operator
  Source: https://github.com/cloudnative-pg/cloudnative-pg
  License: Apache License 2.0
  Copyright: Contributors to CloudNativePG, established as CloudNativePG
             a Series of LF Projects, LLC.

Barman Cloud Plugin
  Source: https://github.com/cloudnative-pg/plugin-barman-cloud
  License: Apache License 2.0
  Copyright: Contributors to CloudNativePG, established as CloudNativePG
             a Series of LF Projects, LLC.

Helm Charts
-----------
We redistribute CloudNativePG Helm charts with modifications to use
pgEdge-built operator images.

Location: charts/cloudnative-pg/
  Source: https://github.com/cloudnative-pg/charts
  License: Apache License 2.0
  Copyright: Contributors to CloudNativePG, established as CloudNativePG
             a Series of LF Projects, LLC.
  Modification: Default image references changed to ghcr.io/pgedge/ registry.

Location: charts/plugin-barman-cloud/
  Source: https://github.com/cloudnative-pg/plugin-barman-cloud
  License: Apache License 2.0
  Copyright: Contributors to CloudNativePG, established as CloudNativePG
             a Series of LF Projects, LLC.
  Modification: Default image references changed to ghcr.io/pgedge/ registry.

Manifests
---------
We redistribute CloudNativePG installation manifests with modifications to use
pgEdge-built operator images.

Location: manifests/cloudnative-pg/
  Source: https://github.com/cloudnative-pg/cloudnative-pg
  License: Apache License 2.0
  Copyright: Contributors to CloudNativePG, established as CloudNativePG
             a Series of LF Projects, LLC.
  Modification: Operator image references changed to ghcr.io/pgedge/ registry.

